  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To gather data essential to evaluate the acceptability and feasibility of a brief, health
      care-based program delivered in routine healthcare visits in low and low-middle income
      countries to promote positive parenting behaviors with the aim to support early child
      development.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
